{"tid":1240722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣好重要！！！] 一齊幫手擺街站，派傳單","createTime":"2019-06-18T12:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T11:49:31.000Z","uid":49456,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c12ce577d99d274efba5f1a6e7f75c906feff1","tid":1240722,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"我認為對上兩次既遊行可以咁震撼<br />\n除左有警犬助攻<br />\n就係全靠眾多巴絲擺街站<br />\n平均每行幾步路就見到有人派傳單，貼街招<br />\n搞到全世界都討論，全世界都關注<br />\n<br />\n離6月21仲有幾日<br />\n<br />\n派傳單其實都幾低成本低風險<br />\n希望大家可以幫手自發去PRINT，自發去派/貼<br />\n<br />\n繼續煲大件事<br />\n<br />\n不過最好約埋朋友仔<br />\n就算有藍絲搞都唔怕<br />\n<br />\n其實之前有組織喺街頭不斷播黑警打人既片係好好<br />\n但普通市民邊有呢D資源 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nANYWAY，以下有兩張EXAMPLE，貼爆18區<br />\n其他款可以上TG搵下<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/589475668207599620/590249330007605258/image0.png?width=1079&amp;height=675\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F589475668207599620%2F590249330007605258%2Fimage0.png%3Fwidth%3D1079%26height%3D675&h=5977ed36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/589475668207599620/590188793055805476/4points_Page7.png?width=895&amp;height=895\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F589475668207599620%2F590188793055805476%2F4points_Page7.png%3Fwidth%3D895%26height%3D895&h=b28ddb50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"700987991712940763f2618c26d0216a08535cfa","tid":1240722,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6439d27364015fc8165c3763ab5dc86f2ba160","tid":1240722,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688c387e